                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Level 9</strong></p>\n<p>A creeping malaise overcomes the afflicted, whose skin develops a sickly pallor.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"disease\" data-pf2-label=\"Resist Disease DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span>;</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 3} (1 day);</p>\n<p>The target can't recover from the drained condition from Abyssal plague until the disease is cured.</p>\n</div>"
